Lets Do the Exploratory Data Analysis

cleaned_possum_filtered <- cleaned_possum %>% select(-c(Pop, sex))
corr_matrix <- cor(cleaned_possum_filtered)
library(htmlwidgets)
if (exists("style_background_gradient", mode = "function")) {
  corr_matrix_styled <- corr_matrix %>%
    htmlwidgets::style_background_gradient(cmap = "coolwarm")
} else {
  library(DT)  
  corr_matrix_styled <- DT::datatable(corr_matrix, options = list(
    pageLength = 20,  
    ordering = FALSE   
  ))
  corr_matrix_styled %>% formatStyle('all', function(x) {
    if (x > 0.5) {
      return(list(color = 'red'))  
    } else if (x < -0.5) {
      return(list(color = 'blue'))  
    }
  })
}
corr_matrix_styled
cleaned_possum_numeric <- cleaned_possum[, sapply(cleaned_possum, is.numeric)]
corr_matrix <- cor(cleaned_possum_numeric)
print(corr_matrix)
